data.Title: The Irishman
data.Description: An aging hitman recalls his time with the mob and the intersecting events with his friend, Jimmy Hoffa, through the 1950-70s.

data.Title: Parasite
data.Description: A poor family, the Kims, con their way into becoming the servants of a rich family, the Parks. But their easy life gets complicated when their deception is threatened with exposure.

data.Title: The Favourite
data.Description: In early 18th century England, a frail Queen Anne occupies the throne and her close friend, Lady Sarah, governs the country in her stead. When a new servant, Abigail, arrives, her charm endears her to Sarah.

data.Title: The Farewell I
data.Description: A Chinese family discovers their grandmother has only a short while left to live and decide to keep her in the dark, scheduling a wedding to gather before she dies.

data.Title: Shoplifters
data.Description: A family of small-time crooks take in a child they find outside in the cold.
